description: We are a limited liability corporation (LLC) operating out of Lancaster, Ohio. As a registered mobile food vendor we have passed all county health inspections for the 2012 festival year and can gear up quickly to serve our fabulous half-pound hot dogs and other menu items. If you don’t see it listed on our Menu page, just ask! Give your special event a festival atmosphere by letting your guests order up hot dogs, brats, hamburgers, and other juicy items directly from our concessions cart! Better yet, book us for tailgating. You buy the supplies, and we’ll do the cooking! Our attached 40-inch outdoor television lets you watch the big game outdoors—get the team spirit without the driving and parking hassles!
name: Dandy Dog Ohio
